"{\"uid\": \"news.cgtn.com-news-2024-08-08-Shanghai-summer-festival-embraces-Olympic-spirit-1vRKVYcXhte-p.html\", \"text\": \"Our Privacy Statement & Cookie Policy  By continuing to browse our site you agree to our use of cookies, revised Privacy Policy and Terms of Use. You can change your cookie settings through your browser.  CGTN  Copied  Embracing the Olympic spirit and the excitement of the Paris Olympics, the \\\"Shanghai Summer\\\" consumption festival is heating up the city's nightlife and giving a boost to the local economy. A trendy new night market along the Xuhui riverside promenade offers an enticing blend of food, culture, sports, and entertainment. With its sports-themed stalls and interactive activities, this festival aims to infuse Shanghai's summer with greater vibrancy.  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466\"}"